rComments: This teacher reads directly off of lecture slides which has absolutely no correlation to the readings she assigns in the textbook. Rarely anything she talks about in lecture is related to the content on the test and the exam. She is extremely unclear about assignment details and does not mark clearly. I would not recommend her to any student.

Coupon system of rewarding class participation is a joke, much like her teach ability. AVOID!
